Text: 3>German : TuneUp Utilities 2011 Build 10.0.3000.101 Final German ( lol i said 2 times about the guide)

Do you have a computer without internet and only for your work? You think it need an maintenance ? Well TuneUp 2011 Portable its the best choice ! Just load the app on your USB Drive ,note a serial,you might need it and youre ready to go.Connect your USB device to that PC and start maintenace.
Turn off internet while you installing ,Block application with your firewall to access and send mail to main server. The main server can infect a tune up file from install.
